text: The canton of Canteleu is an administrative division of the Seine-Maritime department, in northern France. It was created at the French canton reorganisation which came into effect in March 2015. Its seat is in Canteleu.Décret n° 2014-266 du 27 février 2014 portant délimitation des cantons dans le département de la Seine-Maritime It consists of the following communes: #Canteleu #Hautot-sur-Seine #Maromme #Sahurs #Saint-Pierre-de- Manneville #Val-de-la-Haye ==References== Category:Cantons of Seine-Maritime
